M|NRR|tx|```
M|NRR|Star|$6M
M|NRR|Expa|$60K (annual)
M|NRR|Chur|$600K (annual)
M|NRR|Cont|$120K (annual)
M|NRR|Endi|$5.34M
M|NRR|tx|NRR = $5.34M / $6M = 89%
M|NRR|tx|```
M|NRR|al|** NRR <100% = contracting base. Losing rv from existing cs faster than expanding them.
M|Quic|tx|```
M|Quic|tx|Gains = $100K + $5K = $105K
M|Quic|tx|Losses = $50K + $10K = $60K
M|Quic|tx|Quick Ratio = $105K / $60K = 1.75
M|Quic|tx|```
M|Quic|al|** Quick Ratio <2 = leaky bucket. Barely outpacing losses.
