M|ЁЯУК R|tx|**Why is churn increasing?**
M|ЁЯУК R|it|pd qual degrading?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|Wrong cs segment (poor fit)?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|Onboarding failures?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|Competitive pressure?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|Pricing too hi for value delivered?
M|ЁЯУК R|tx|**Why are newer cohorts worse?**
M|ЁЯУК R|it|cs acquisition qual degrading?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|pd changes breaking key use cases?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|Support qual declining as company scales?
M|ЁЯУК R|tx|**Why no expansion?**
M|ЁЯУК R|it|No upsell paths in packaging?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|cs not reaching "aha moment" where they'd expand?
M|ЁЯУК R|it|pd doesn't grow w/ cs needs?
M|ЁЯУК R|tx|---
M|ЁЯЫС S|tx|Do NOT increase mk spend until retention is fixed. Scaling a leaky bucket just burns cash faster.
M|ЁЯЫС S|**Wh|** At current churn rates, every dollar spent acquiring cs leaks out within 12 months. Fix the bucket first.
M|ЁЯЫС S|tx|---
M|ЁЯФе P|**In|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Run churn interviews w/ 20-30 churned cs
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Segment churn by cohort, use case, cs size
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|3. Identify top 3 churn reasons
M|ЁЯФе P|**Qu|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Improve onboarding (70% of churn happens in first 60 days)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Proactive support for at-risk accounts (identify usage drop-offs)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|3. Re-engage dormant accounts before they churn
M|ЁЯФе P|**Go|** Reduce logo churn from 6% to 4% within 8 weeks, target 3% within 16 weeks.
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|---
M|ЁЯФе P|**Cr|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Introduce premium tier (advanced features)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Usage-based add-ons (additional seats, integrations)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|3. Cross-sell complementary features
M|ЁЯФе P|**Id|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Which cs use pd heavily? (Target for upsell)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Which cs hit usage limits? (Offer expansion)
M|ЁЯФе P|**Go|** Increase expansion MRR from 1% to 5% of base within 12 weeks.
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|---
M|ЁЯФе P|**Tr|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Weekly cohort retention dashboards
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Compare new cohorts to baseline (75% at Month 6)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|3. Don't scale until new cohorts retain BETTER than old cohorts
M|ЁЯФе P|**Pr|**
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|1. Fix onboarding (time-to-value)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|2. Improve core use cases (reduce churn reasons)
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|3. Add sticky features (integrations, data accumulation)
M|ЁЯФе P|**Go|** Reverse cohort degradation tn within 16 weeks. New cohorts shd retain at 75%+ by Month 6.
M|ЁЯФе P|tx|---
M|тЬЕ Su|Do N|
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] Logo churn <4% monthly (ideally <3%)
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] rv churn <5% monthly
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] NRR >100% (expansion exceeds churn)
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] Quick Ratio >2.5 (ideally >4)
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] New cohorts retain same or better than old cohorts
M|тЬЕ Su|it|[ ] Expansion MRR >5% of total MRR
M|тЬЕ Su|**Ti|** 12-16 weeks to fix. Then reassess scaling.
M|тЬЕ Su|tx|---
